dc_title_s: Cape May Point, Cape May Co., N.J.
dc_description_s: "Aug. 1890." Includes key, streets and specials index and text. "3993." Historic Maps copy has sheets 1-4 of New Jersey coast series, vol 4., showing Cape May Point, N.J. Historic Maps copy has index sheet of series, with title: Insurance maps of the New Jersey coast, vol. 4, in 40 sheets (#3993); sheet includes location maps, key and index. Historic Maps copy has stamp of Map Division, Library of Congress, dated Dec. 6, 1890.
dc_publisher_s: New York : Sanborn-Perris Map Co., Limited, 1890.
dc_subject_sm: Fire insurance maps—New Jersey—Cape May Point—1890
